Description:

Extend ctl_mboxlist -d/-u to deal with all fields in mboxlist

(N.B. This means uidvalidity, createdmodseq, foldermodseq, legacy_specialuse, mtime from struct mailbox_entry)

Config changes:

None

Upgrade instructions:

This change makes possible to follow the procedure for switching improved_mboxlist_sort described in docsrc/imap/developer/thoughts/improved_mboxlist_sort.rst
